<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">Le congiunzioni</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        93
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Story Introduction -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Luigi scrive un breve tema sul suo amico Joy.
    </p>
    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-blue-300">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
        Nella bella copia, Luigi ha unito le frasi con le congiunzioni.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Le congiunzioni <strong>e, o, oppure, ma, però, perciò, allora, infatti, cioè...</strong> collegano due elementi di una frase (<em>Joy è simpatico e allegro.</em>) o due frasi indipendenti (<em>Joy parla e ride</em>) e sono dette <strong class="text-blue-600">coordinative</strong>.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Le congiunzioni <strong>che, se, quando, mentre, perché, perciò, quindi, siccome, poiché, anche se, benché...</strong> collegano due frasi dipendenti (<em>Joy arrivò benché avesse perso il treno</em>) e sono dette <strong class="text-green-600">subordinative</strong>.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Completa le frasi con la congiunzione adatta. Scegli fra:
    </h2>

    <div class="mb-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-yellow-200">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-base md:text-lg text-center font-semibold text-blue-700">
        <div>perché</div>
        <div>ma</div>
        <div>perciò</div>
        <div>però</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Mangio qualcosa</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perché" data-correct-answer="perché" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">ho fame.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• C'è rumore</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perciò" data-correct-answer="perciò" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">non ti sento.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Io parlo</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ma" data-correct-answer="ma" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">tu non ascolti.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Queen è orgogliosa</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="però" data-correct-answer="però" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">dolce.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Sottolinea le congiunzioni <span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-green-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle"></span> e indica se sono coordinative (C) o subordinative (S).
    </h2>

    <!-- Color Selector (hidden for mono-color) -->
    <div class="hidden">
      <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-300"
           data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox"
           data-color="green">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Mi sto divertendo <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">quindi</span> resterò ancora.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_1" value="C" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">C</span>
            </label>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_1" value="S" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">S</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Ho acquistato una sciarpa <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">e</span> un cappello.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_2" value="C" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">C</span>
            </label>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_2" value="S" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">S</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Tommy ha mal di gola <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">perché</span> ha preso freddo.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_3" value="C" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">C</span>
            </label>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_3" value="S" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">S</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Sono in ritardo <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">ma</span> sto arrivando.</span>
          <div class="flex gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_4" value="C" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">C</span>
            </label>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
              <input type="checkbox" name="ex2_4" value="S" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span class="font-semibold">S</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi pp. 178-179</p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
